      "text": " **Theorem 1** (Hasse-Weil bound). Let  $\\mathscr{C}$  be a non-singular, absolutely irreducible projective curve over  $\\mathbb{F}_q$  and let  $N_{\\mathscr{C}} = |\\mathscr{C}(\\mathbb{F}_q)|$  be the number of  $\\mathbb{F}_q$ -rational points of  $\\mathscr{C}$ . Then,",
